    <ThingDef ParentName="ResourceBase" Name="GW_STC_Fragment">
        <defName>GW_STC_Fragment</defName>
        <label>STC fragment</label>
        <description>A hard-copy printout from a Standard Template Construct system, a manufacturing computer database from the Dark Age of Technology. Such databases are long decayed and destroyed, but the printouts produced by them contain powerful secrets. \n\nThe technology-worshipping Adeptus Mechanicus hold these printouts in great regard, and seek to acquire them in any way possible. Finding an intact STC system would be equivalent to discovering the font of all knowledge, and bloody campaigns have been waged over mere rumors of such a system.</description>
